data.description: Incredible corner lot, open living pantry, just over a mile to Hwy 169 and roughly 2 miles to Collinsville Schools or Rejoice Christian Schools! Both aerobic AND traditional septic to add future mobility if desired. Electric Heater coil under home to prevent freezing 220 camper hook up on property! New Mobile moved to lot in 2018.
